  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BreadthFirstLayout
    Layouts the features at the feature diagram using a breadth first search.
    DepthFirstLayout
    Layouts the features at the feature diagram using a depth first search.
    FeatureDiagramLayoutHelper
    A helper class for the feature diagram layout.
    FeatureDiagramLayoutManager
    Calculates locations for all features in the feature diagram.
    FeatureModelLayout
    Encapsulates layout functionality for the feature model.
    FTreeLayout
    Uses abego Tree Layout libary to create a graphical Feature Tree Layout

    GFTreeForTreeLayout
    Provides the getParent and getChildrem methods of the graphical representation of a Feature to abego library
    LayoutableFeature
    A feature representation for layout.
    LevelOrderLayout
    Layouts the features at the feature diagram using a reverse level order search.
    ManualLayout
    Layouts the features at the feature diagram using their saved Positions.
    VerticalLayout
    Ordering features from left to right without any intersections or overlapping
